instructions: put the plate on the charger
put the napkin on the plate so that it's up and down in the middle of the plate
put the dinner fork on the left of the plate with the prongs facing up
put the salad fork to the left of the dinner fork with the prongs facing up
put the dinner knife to the right of the plate with the blade facing the plate
put the tea spoon to the right of the knife with the bowl at the top
put the soup spoon to the right of the tea spoon with the bowl facing up
put the water glass above and slightly to the left of the knife
put the wine glass to the immediate right of the water glass
move the wine glass so it's closer to the spoons
put the coffee cup to the right of the wine glass
put the bread plate above the forks
put the butter knife horizontally on top of the bread plate
put the dessert fork next to the bread plate so that the tongs are pointing toward the water glass
put the dessert spoon under the dessert fork so the bowl is facing the bread plate
